pageContext.claim: “I asked Vice President Mike Pence to call up the head of Honduras, to call up the heads of all -- he called them. He said, 'Listen, we don't want you to allow the formation of caravans in your country. We pay you hundreds of millions of dollars a year, which is probably just stolen.'”
pageContext.analysis: Trump claims without evidence that U.S. aid sent to Honduras "is probably just stolen."
